h2. Summary

Currentlly, confluence does not have the option to bulk import documentation. Webdav and Import a text file is not available for confluence cloud.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *Confluence Cloud*. Using *Confluence Server*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/CONFSERVER-45687].
  {panel}

The Macro Task Report is to be supplemented with the variable '@self' to the parameter 'Assigned to' and 'Created by'.
This allows you to create a parent dashboard for a space where the user can see his Confluence and JIRA tasks without any user creating their own dashboard.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *Confluence Cloud*. Using *Confluence Server*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/CONFSERVER-45682].
