On this [link |https://documentation.cpanel.net/display/EA4/Modify+Apache+Virtual+Hosts+with+Include+Files] [link |https://documentation.cpanel.net/display/EA4/Modify+Apache+Virtual+Hosts+with+Include+Files]there is no info that config would not work until run of:
{code:java}
/scripts/rebuildhttpdconf{code}

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
